author: stsp
msg: Improve handling of temporary allocations in the mergeinfo parsing code.
(parse_revision_line): Rename the POOL parameter to SCRATCH_POOL.
Use the scratch pool for temporary allocations. Store results in the
pool which the provided mergeinfo hash was allocated in.
(parse_top): Use an iterpool while calling parse_revision_line() in a loop.
